<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In the function limit() in the class Zend_Db_Adapter_Pdo_Mssql there is a problem with the usage of an uninitialized variable in line 137. The line looks like this:</p>

<p>$order = implode(',', $parts['order']);</p>

<p>The variable $parts has not been initialized in the context of the function limit() nor was it passed to the function as a parameter.</p>

    </div>
